Playboy - January 2014  ZA

164 Pages | True PDF | English | 61 MB 


Playboy Men's Magazine features monthly interviews of notable public figures, such as artists, architects, economists, composers, conductors, film directors, journalists, novelists, playwrights, religious figures, politicians, athletes and race car drivers. The magazine generally reflects a liberal editorial stance.
